UHE-101 cream, 1% ("UHE-101") is being developed for the topical treatment of acne vulgaris.

 The purpose of this study is to compare the safety and efficacy of twice daily topical application of UHE-101 cream for 12 weeks to its vehicle cream in subjects with facial acne vulgaris.

